{
  "title": "Rich Buttery Greek Vegetable Stir Fry",
  "description": "A hearty and comforting Greek dish featuring garlic and a variety of vegetables, perfect for a sick day, and suitable for a Jain-friendly diet. This rich and buttery stir-fry is dense with flavor and sure to satisfy.",
