  "instructions": [
    "Melt 2 tablespoons of butter in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook for 3-4 minutes, until translucent.",
    "Add the sliced zucchini and bell peppers, and cook for 5 minutes, until tender.",
    "Add the halved cherry tomatoes and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in the pitted kalamata olives and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Stir in the remaining 2 tablespoons of butter until melted and well combined.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley."
